**Violation**

```vhdl
entity FIFO is
  port (
    I_DATA : in std_logic_vector(31 downto 0)
  );
end entity fifo;

architecture rtl of fifo is

begin

   register <= i_data;

end architecture rtl;
```

**Fix**

```vhdl
entity FIFO is
  port (
    I_DATA : in std_logic_vector(31 downto 0)
  );
end entity fifo;

architecture rtl of fifo is

begin

   register <= I_DATA;

end architecture rtl;
```

